00:37:48,000 --> 00:37:52,600
the essential continuity between geochemistry and biochemistry.

534
00:37:52,600 --> 00:37:57,400
That by itself would not be enough to judge whether the presence of life on earth is surprising

535
00:37:57,400 --> 00:37:58,640
or inevitable.

